 request, including RDT&E and procurement of prototype units. The Department will certify Future Years Defense Program funding in a future budget request.

 The total cost of the MW/MT - MEO Epoch 2 Middle Tier of Acquisition effort is 3,846.5M, including RDT&E and procurement of prototype units. The MW/MT - MEO
 Epoch 2 program is fully funded across the Future Years Defense Program.


