Remarks

E. Acquisition Strategy
Space: The Resilient Missile Warning, Missile Tracking Medium Earth Orbit initiative began in FY 2019 as Next Gen Overhead Persistent Infrared "Block 1 Prototype”
under the Next Gen Overhead Persistent Infrared Space Modernization Initiative PE1206442SF. Six missile track custody prototype contracts were competitively
awarded under this effort which utilized a multi-phased contracting strategy to field an on-orbit Missile Track Custody Demonstration or the Missile Track Custody

