E. Acquisition Strategy
All contracts funded in this program will be awarded using competitive procedures to the maximum extent possible.
Space Superiority and R&D Intelligence Development: Single Delivery, Cost-Plus-Fixed-Fee (CPFF), advisory and assistance contractor supporting development and
implementation efforts, such as engineering architectural development and planning. Prime contractor is Cherokee LLC.

 Architecture upgrades to support SDA, SSDP, and Space Superiority: Multiple Delivery, CPFF integration contract for acquiring, integration, installation and testing of
 ISR collection assets, as well as Requirements Management Framework (RMF) certifications to operate. Prime contractor is CACI or competitively selected successor.

 Data Analysis, Production Development, Test Support for R&D: Multiple Delivery, CPFF production contract supporting vulnerabilities analysis of ISR collected material.
 Prime Contractor is Booz Allen Hamilton.




