Title: Rapid Resilient Command and Control (R2C2) Pre-Operations (Pre-Ops) Support                                                    44.972        0.000        0.000
Description: Maintain hardware and software baselines, update software licenses, integrate cybersecurity, and provide help-desk
operations with associated training.

FY 2025 Plans:
Continue pre-ops support activities and facilities for protect and defend mission partners using R2C2 satellite operations ground
segment services (SatOps) to include maintaining software baselines, expanding commercial cloud environments, supporting
private cloud environments, updating software licenses, facilitating user engagements, and continuing 24x7 help desk operations,
associated training, and cybersecurity support. Continue service center capabilities to support mission partners developing,
integrating, testing, and operating R2C2 SatOps services. Accomplish necessary infrastructure technical refresh, patching, and
cybersecurity updates. Continue support of antenna networking services.
FY 2026 Plans:
N/A
