technical refresh, patching, and cybersecurity updates. Will continue support of antenna networking services. Will initiate life cycle
sustainment activities for R2C2 SatOps C2 services in support of ongoing protect and defend missions.
FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY 2026 Cloud Infrastructure and Platform/Antenna Services funding increased by 49.950 million due to transfer from PE
1206770SF, Enterprise Ground Services. This includes a reduction for Advisory and Assistance Services efficiencies. FY25
funding was in PE 1206857SF, Space Rapid Capabilities Office due to a congressionally directed transfer.
