Description: The program maintains existing capability for the National Space Defense Center (NSDC), Combined Space
Operations Center (CSpOC) and other C2 centers. These tasks include maintaining the Commercial Off The Shelf (COTS)
software database, removing, and canceling decommissioned systems and unused tools, adding new tools required for ongoing
support of the system, maintaining data support systems, and maintaining day-to-day software operations which continuously
ensures and optimizes reliability, security, resiliency, availability, flexibility and scalability of the warfighter tools.

