E. Acquisition Strategy
Following a reverse industry day and several post-event engagements with various industry and USG partners, the Secure Enclave program office gained substantial
insight regarding investment requirements and opportunities. With this insight, the program office developed an informed pilot project acquisition strategy which
allows for a flexible approach to cover key use cases, capability testing, and intellectual property development to accelerate the adoption of SOTA microelectronics.
Additionally, the program office continues to work closely with the vendor as a sole source to efficiently refine production capacity investment and integration to support
the nation's most sensitive warfighting capabilities.




